{"tid":1855061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國封關？今個周日起禁止曾踏足中國之旅客入境","createTime":"2020-02-01T00:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T04:53:15.000Z","uid":41818,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c0608efa2845a4be8ec1b32d8e1c90642444ff22","tid":1855061,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T00:34:50.000Z","msg":"美國政府宣佈，因應武漢肺炎確診個案進一步擴散，總統特朗普已簽署行政命令，在下周日（2月2日）東岸時間下午5時起，禁止任何在過去14日內到訪中國的外國人，入境美國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而美國公民的直接親屬，或持有美國永久居留身份（綠卡持有人）的直接親屬，則仍然可以入境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，過去14日內曾到訪中國湖北省的美國公民，需要被強制接受隔離14日。而從中國其他城市出發、返回美國的公民，會被分流到境內7個特設機場接受檢疫，才可入境。當中包括紐約約翰甘迺迪國際機場、芝加哥奧黑爾國際機場及三藩市國際機場等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n截至今日，美國已確診7宗感染新型冠狀病毒個案。美國衞生部門官員表示，國內爆發疫症的機會很低，以上措施是為了確保爆發疫症的機會維持低水平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200201/RMVGDWGXVKY6QJCMGR4EXSY5JQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200201%2FRMVGDWGXVKY6QJCMGR4EXSY5JQ%2F&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=8481aaea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200201%2FRMVGDWGXVKY6QJCMGR4EXSY5JQ%2F&h=08a54b7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200201/RMVGDWGXVKY6QJCMGR4EXSY5JQ/</a>"},{"pid":"0651961e76a1f508ab36e003ca1c7af318c860bc","tid":1855061,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T00:35:34.000Z","msg":"The United States announced Friday it would be taking new measures to combat a coronavirus outbreak, including denying entry to foreign nationals who had recently visited China and imposing 14-day quarantines on American citizens returning from mainland China.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/coronavirus-china-live-updates/2020/01/31/eeac61b6-442b-11ea-b503-2b077c436617_story.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fcoronavirus-china-live-updates%2F2020%2F01%2F31%2Feeac61b6-442b-11ea-b503-2b077c436617_story.html&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=1f74de03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/coronavirus-china-live-updates/2020/01/31/eeac61b6-442b-11ea-b503-2b077c436617_story.html</a>"},{"pid":"14b0270e2765ebddbfe8c23e6eea56fbf8d9098f","tid":1855061,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T00:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83a6dccf72c08298cd410a4e9994f61f38162c0","tid":1855061,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T00:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04dfc23901522ce77ae197660aedfcfddc72a39","tid":1855061,"uid":173271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T00:41:36.000Z","msg":"封多一重，要橫掃全地球難度增加了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da5a6eb0e53e606cf7bbc50aa00b4ee921e5c6c","tid":1855061,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T00:43:11.000Z","msg":"咁香港係咪唔算？"},{"pid":"bc8fc5a82dedf55a5eb5218440df24bd311ed960","tid":1855061,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T00:43:55.000Z","msg":"鎖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f485a416b0169ad363b86615c7871cd8becc160","tid":1855061,"uid":275688,"like":1,"dislike